// Fields:
//   kind           ProviderArtifactKind enumerator
//   command_kind   CommandKind enumerator for the CLI-facing emission hook
//   artifact_type  durable_store_import model type
//   builder        internal provider pipeline node builder
//   printer        stable artifact printer facade
//   command_token  stable CLI command token that emits this artifact
//   visibility     Public (top-level meaningful pipeline output) or
//                  Internal (intermediate pipeline node)
//   order          provider-local CLI/list order derived from DAG locality

